+# Specialist capability growth — Projects closed loop
+
+## Correlated path
+
+```text
+0285 closed capability-growth evidence
+→ r2 non-authoritative review projection
+→ r5 digest-bound publication plan
+→ r6 explicit operator authorization and execution/replay
+→ r7 query-only readback
+→ r8 pure correlation proof
+```
+
+The r8 proof verifies the same repository, Issue, ProjectV2 item, revision,
+decision, `sql_ref`, marker, comment digest, nine field values and
+`plan_digest`.
+
+## Closure levels
+
+A local fixture can close the deterministic contract but cannot prove a live
+GitHub deployment. Deployment closure additionally requires a successful
+`live_query_only` r7 readback. The r8 smoke never performs network access.
+
+## Authority
+
+- GitHub Projects remains a workflow/review projection.
+- SQL remains the durable authority.
+- Scheduler remains the only orchestrator.
+- Qdrant remains projection/recall only.
+- Copilot remains advisory.
